    COUNT(*) AS number_of_paintings
FROM paintings
WHERE inception IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY strftime('%Y', inception)
ORDER BY year;

2. Group the results by year
3. Count the number of paintings in each group
4. Order the results by year for better readability

The SQL query will use GROUP BY on the extracted year and COUNT(*) to get the number of paintings per year.
